NUMBER 1067
NAME Gem Market
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
BUY_JEWELRY
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
More of a wholesale market than a regular jewelry store, the interior of
the building is filled with numerous tables all creaking under the weight
of bags, sacks, chests and other containers that hold gems of all kinds.
Behind the tables various representativies of the shop haggle loudly with
buyers and sellers. Two burly, and VERY tough looking guards keep a careful
eye on the customers. An arch leads back out to the shopping arcade.
*DESCRIPTION_END
