NUMBER 1068
NAME Shopping Arcade
ASTRAL
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The crowded street parts before one particular building, a towering stone
structure with the sculpture of a ferocious Red Dragon extending outwards,
from above a jagged opening in the building's front. Raucous voices, and
the occasional yelp of pain, emanate from within the building. The opening
was formed when the crew contracted to construct the tavern forgot to put
an entrance in and the outraged tavern owner used the head of the crew
foreman to make the entrance. At least, thats what the tales relate...
*DESCRIPTION_END
