NUMBER 2238
NAME Red Dragon Tavern
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A dull gray haze drifts slowly across the noisy den, wrapping its tendrils
around the large wooden poles that support the high ceiling. Pushed up
against the poles are scarred wooden tables with intermingled blood and ale
stains streaking across their surface. Wide stools are pushed up against
the tables and the long bar that stretches across the east wall of the
tavern. The patrons of the bar, predominantly drakin, watch each newcomer
warily then return to their drinks and conversations. A battered wooden
sign, on the wall behind the bar, displays the drinks and food available.
Raucous patrons stand around a railing in the northernmost section of the,
looking down into a pit of sorts. A stairway next to the railing leads
down into the pit, and a door leads to the healers.
*DESCRIPTION_END
CALL 19
