NUMBER 2239
NAME Red Dragon, pit
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Sputtering torches cast a greasy light over the sand-covered floor of the
Red Dragon Taverns' brawling pit. The amount of dried blood coating the
sand gives evidence that it is a frequently used place. Darkness fills the
edges of the pit, which is a good thing considering the gruesome shapes
that are hidden in the dark. A stairway climbs out of the pit to the
tavern proper.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 81 ADJ1=355 VAL2=2238
VARIABLE shaido
VARIABLE shaido1
VARIABLE shaido2
IFENTRY
  ECHO PLAYER A voice speaks in your mind, "Choose your Shaido, Easy, Hard or Expert"
ENDIF
IFSAY easy
 ADD shaido 1
  IFVAR shaido =< 10
    ECHO ALL A goblin is thrown out into the pit.
    GENMON 81
  ENDIF
   IFVAR shaido > 10
     ECHO ALL A voice shouts out, "Sorry, no more goblins today, we've killed the last one."
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFSAY hard
  ADD shaido1 1
  IFVAR shaido1 =< 5
    ECHO ALL A greater ghoul shuffles out into the center of the pit.
    GENMON 183
  ENDIF
   IFVAR shaido1 > 5
     ECHO ALL A voice shouts out, "Run out of the ghouls, we're gonna have to animate some more, come back later."
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY expert
  ADD shaido2 1
    IFVAR shaido2 =< 3
      ECHO ALL A werewolf snarls as it leaps into the pit.
      GENMON 278
    ENDIF
      IFVAR shaido2 > 3
        ECHO ALL A voice shouts out, nervously, "Damn it all, they're tough to capture, we'll have to go find some more. Come back later."
     ENDIF
ENDIF
;
