*DESCRIPTION_START
A sense of awe fills you as you stand in the center of this marble
chamber. Intricate swirls of gold fleck the marble walls and floor,
combining to form ornate Drakin words and pictorials. Individual
streaks of gold flow around the arches that lead into the private
chambers of the Elders. Across from the arches is a white arch
that leads back out into the castle proper. Set against one wall is
an ornate table made from black onyx.
