NUMBER 1502
NAME San Ulnar
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Peace and stength are upon you as you enter this house, you seem to
become one with the atmosphere in here. This place exudes magick, the
air almost crackling with it as you move about. Items of great power
adorne the walls, books and ancient scrolls fill the shelves surrounding
the fireplace. An ornate wooden desk, covered with parchments, sits in
one corner along with a large mirmach chair, they both look as if many
hous have been spent using them. Most of this home seems devoted to
study and it is absolutly silent in here. The other portion of this home
holds an enourmous bed that looks quite comfortable, but rarely used.
Above the bed hangs a large portrait of a Drakin, encased in a golden
frame. Next to the bed is a small couch.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 1501
