Your eyes are drawn to three walls of ceiling height weapons racks, enough
to arm an entire division of Two-weapon Drakin warriors. A sign on the last
wall reads "The best Defense is Offense, Offense, Offense!"  A destroyed
battle dummy slumps in the middle of the room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 1501
