*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Nearly 150 feet long, and 30 feet high, Thunderchild hovers in place
about 10 feet above the hangar floor. Thinly hammered steel plates cover
the entire outer hull, adding a protective layer of armoring. The proud
figure of Folknar, Ancestor of War, cuts through the air ahead of the
ship. Even in the still air of the hangar, the sails billow as if the
ship were impatient to be on its way.
*DESCRIPTION_END
