NUMBER 1510
NAME Thunderchild, Forecastle
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
Standing on the forecastle deck, you have an unobstructed view of your
surroundings as well as what is directly ahead. The steel-sheathed
foremast rises from the center of the deck, and overhead, the sails
billow and snap even in the slightest breeze. Extending boldly from the
prow is the familiar carved figure of the Ancestor, Folknar. An inclined
ramp leads back down to the quarterdeck.
*DESCRIPTION_END
